    <title>Corsair now has a gaming keyboard and mouse for the Mac</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="The Corsair K65 Plus wireless keyboard and the M75 wireless mouse in glacier blue on a desk." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8VlKlDqGGOH0nGLwFTfwhRC9Qqk=/0x0:2500x1667/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73731830/corsair1.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;em&gt;Corsair has upgraded its K65 Plus wireless keyboard and M75 wireless mouse so they’re Mac compatible with new colorways.&lt;/em&gt; | Image: Corsair&lt;/figcaption&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;

  &lt;p id="OiQjtB"&gt;Corsair has &lt;a href="https://go.corsair.com/c/482924/490888/8513?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.corsair.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-release%2Fcorsair-unveils-exclusive-award-winning-k65-plus-wireless-keyboard-and-m75-wireless-gaming-mouse-colorways-for-mac%3Futm_source%3D95368%26utm_medium%3DAffiliate%26utm_campaign%3D1498468_Main%2520Page%26utm_content%3DCorsair%26clickid%3DVQF2hWUIXxyKWEx3n%253AQzIWnLUkCQ3JSfPy2CWc0%26utm_coupon%3D%26irgwc%3D1&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;announced an updated version&lt;/a&gt; of the K65 Plus wireless keyboard it &lt;a href="https://go.corsair.com/c/482924/490888/8513?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.corsair.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-release%2Fcorsair-launches-new-75-keyboard-for-enthusiast-gamers&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;debuted earlier this year&lt;/a&gt; that’s now compatible with the Mac. It’s joined by a new version of Corsair’s M75 wireless mouse, and both peripherals are available in Mac-exclusive colors including glacier blue and a white version the company calls frost.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="hfdX3O"&gt;The frost versions of the &lt;a href="https://www.apple.com/shop/product/HRYZ2ZM/A/corsair-k65-plus-wireless-mechanical-gaming-keyboard-for-mac"&gt;K65 Plus wireless keyboard&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://www.apple.com/shop/product/HRYT2ZM/A/corsair-m75-wireless-lightweight-rgb-gaming-mouse"&gt;M75 wireless mouse&lt;/a&gt; are available now from Apple’s online and retail stores for $179.95 and $129.95, respectively. The glacier blue versions will be available for the same price, but at a later date.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class="e-image"&gt;
        
      &lt;cite&gt;Image: Corsair&lt;/cite&gt;
      &lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Mac version of the Corsair K65 Plus wireless keyboard is exclusively available in glacier blue and frost (white)...&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;
